HR NO. 388 ENROLLED
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Wade Dubea on the occasion of his
retirement from state service; does hereby express enduring appreciation for his dedication
to Louisiana's forest resource; and does hereby extend sincere wishes that he remain
prosperous in his endeavors.
